WEBVTT

00:03.034 --> 00:04.675
WHERE´S CARMEN´S DIARY?

00:06.707 --> 00:09.009
I KNOW SEEING ZACK
BEHIND OUR BACKS IS HUGE,

00:09.009 --> 00:11.011
BUT I DON´T
FEEL GOOD ABOUT THIS.

00:11.011 --> 00:12.483
YOU HAVE A BETTER WAY
TO FIND OUT

00:12.483 --> 00:14.014
WHAT ELSE
SHE´S LYING ABOUT?

00:14.014 --> 00:16.047
BUT ONCE WE
OPEN HER DIARY,

00:16.047 --> 00:18.289
WE´LL BE BREAKING A BOND
OF TRUST.

00:18.289 --> 00:21.752
IF THEY´RE HAVING SEX, ANGIE,
YOU COULD BE A GRANDMA.

00:21.752 --> 00:24.155
I´LL RIP THAT LOCK OFF
WITH MY TEETH.

00:26.627 --> 00:29.200
MOM, DAD,
I DON´T WANT TO --

00:29.200 --> 00:32.263
HEY.
WHAT´S HAPPENING?

00:32.263 --> 00:35.035
HOW OFTEN
DO YOU GUYS DO THIS?

00:35.035 --> 00:38.309
EVERY TIME
THERE´S AN EARTHQUAKE.

00:38.309 --> 00:39.710
CAN YOU FEEL THAT?

00:41.242 --> 00:42.713
AFTERSHOCK.

00:45.076 --> 00:47.078
I THOUGHT YOU
LEFT FOR SCHOOL.

00:47.078 --> 00:48.579
I CHANGED MY MIND.

00:48.579 --> 00:50.181
WELL,
WHAT´S THE MATTER?

00:50.181 --> 00:51.182
I DON´T WANT TO GO.

00:51.182 --> 00:52.623
IF I FAILED,

00:52.623 --> 00:54.725
I´M JUST GONNA HAVE TO
SIT THERE LIKE AN IDIOT

00:54.725 --> 00:58.329
WHILE EVERYONE ELSE IS ALL HAPPY
SIGNING THEIR YEARBOOKS.

00:58.329 --> 01:02.263
OKAY, WELL,
YOU LISTEN TO ME, MAX.

01:02.263 --> 01:04.735
OKAY, YOU COULD
FAIL THE FIFTH GRADE EVERY YEAR

01:04.735 --> 01:06.837
UNTIL WE´RE OLD
AND SENILE, OKAY?

01:06.837 --> 01:09.540
THEN YOU COULD DRESS US UP
IN FUNNY CLOTHES

01:09.540 --> 01:13.474
AND CHARGE THE NEIGHBORHOOD KIDS
TO RIDE US.

01:13.474 --> 01:17.208
AND YOU WILL STILL
BE A BETTER CHILD THAN CARMEN.

01:17.208 --> 01:19.850
COME ON,
GO TO SCHOOL.

01:19.850 --> 01:21.552
OH, WAIT, WAIT.

01:21.552 --> 01:23.654
HEY, WHERE´S
CARMEN´S DIARY?

01:23.654 --> 01:26.117
TAPED UNDER HER DESK.

01:26.117 --> 01:28.289
MAX!

01:28.289 --> 01:29.660
READING SOMEONE´S DIARY

01:29.660 --> 01:32.363
IS A HORRIBLE INVASION
OF THEIR PRIVACY.

01:32.363 --> 01:36.096
WHAT´S HORRIBLE
IS PAGE 73.

01:36.096 --> 01:38.129
I MEAN, I´VE SEEN CARMEN
CLEAN HER EARS --

01:38.129 --> 01:41.632
WHY WOULD SOMEONE WANT TO PUT
THEIR TONGUE IN THERE?

01:43.374 --> 01:44.675
WHAT DOES IT SAY?

01:44.675 --> 01:47.107
I´M TRYING TO FIND
SOMETHING ABOUT ZACK.

01:49.380 --> 01:50.811
[ SIGHS ]

01:50.811 --> 01:52.313
WHAT?

01:52.313 --> 01:54.515
OH, MY GOD.
WHAT?!

01:54.515 --> 01:58.319
DID SHE SLEEP WITH HIM?
IS SHE ON DRUGS?

01:58.319 --> 02:00.651
"BIG NEWS
AT THE LOPEZ HOUSE --

02:00.651 --> 02:03.794
"DAD BOUGHT ANOTHER
STUPID FOOTBALL JERSEY.

02:03.794 --> 02:07.328
"HELLO, OLD MAN,
YOU DON´T PLAY FOR THE RAIDERS.

02:07.328 --> 02:10.231
YOU NEVER DID,
AND YOU NEVER COULD."

02:11.862 --> 02:13.604
I COULD´VE
BEEN IN THE SPECIAL TEAMS

02:13.604 --> 02:15.306
IF I HADN´T
HURT MY KNEE STRETCHING.

02:15.306 --> 02:17.208
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

02:21.242 --> 02:22.573
LOOK AT THIS.

02:22.573 --> 02:25.176
SHE WAS TALKING ABOUT ZACK
OVER A MONTH AGO.

02:25.176 --> 02:28.479
OKAY, WELL, FIND THE LAST THING
SHE WROTE ABOUT HIM.

02:28.479 --> 02:30.781
"I LOVE ZACK SO MUCH,

02:30.781 --> 02:33.924
"AND I KNOW HE WANTS
MY FIRST TIME TO BE SPECIAL,

02:33.924 --> 02:36.657
"BUT I DON´T THINK THE BACK
OF HIS TRUCK IS ROMANTIC

02:36.657 --> 02:39.830
NO MATTER HOW MANY PILLOWS
HE HAS BACK THERE."

02:42.193 --> 02:45.196
HEY, MAN, I THOUGHT WE
TOLD YOU TO GO TO SCHOOL.

02:45.196 --> 02:48.499
I KNOW, BUT YOU
CAN GO THROUGH MY ROOM NOW.

02:49.700 --> 02:52.343
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

03:03.183 --> 03:10.221
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

03:39.390 --> 03:40.391
OHH!

03:41.452 --> 03:44.755
OHH, MY GOD,
WHAT IS THAT SMELL?

03:45.556 --> 03:46.527
[ SNIFFS ]

03:50.831 --> 03:53.233
HELLO, BENITA.

03:54.505 --> 03:57.568
PLEASE HEAR ME OUT.

03:57.568 --> 04:00.441
I KNOW POSTPONING OUR MARRIAGE
PUT A TERRIBLE HURT ON YOU,

04:00.441 --> 04:02.543
AND I´M GONNA REGRET THAT
AS LONG AS I LIVE,

04:02.543 --> 04:04.775
BUT I NEEDED
SOME TIME TO THINK.

04:06.977 --> 04:08.449
I NEEDED TO BE ALONE,

04:08.449 --> 04:10.250
SO I WANDERED
THE DESERT

04:10.250 --> 04:13.684
FOR FOUR DAYS
AND FOUR NIGHTS.

04:13.684 --> 04:17.428
YOU KNOW, LIKE THE CHOSEN PEOPLE
DID, BUT SHORTER.

04:18.729 --> 04:20.761
AND THAT´S WHEN IT
HAPPENED TO ME.

04:20.761 --> 04:24.295
I WAS SITTING ON THIS ROCK,
SWEATING AND MEDITATING,

04:24.295 --> 04:25.736
WHEN, ALL OF A SUDDEN,

04:25.736 --> 04:28.499
A BUNCH OF KIDS
WITH GLOW STICKS AND PACIFIERS

04:28.499 --> 04:31.442
CAME OUT OF NOWHERE
AND STARTED DANCING AROUND ME.

04:31.442 --> 04:33.544
THAT´S WHEN I KNEW
WHAT I WANTED.

04:33.544 --> 04:36.407
FIRST, TO GET THE HELL
OUT OF THERE.

04:38.809 --> 04:40.681
THEN, TO MARRY YOU.

04:46.657 --> 04:47.818
[ GROANS ]

04:51.061 --> 04:53.364
[ Straining ]
HAD IT COMIN´.

04:53.594 --> 04:55.796
OUT!

04:56.567 --> 04:58.529
I´LL LEAVE,
BUT THIS ISN´T OVER.

04:58.529 --> 05:01.301
I KNOW YOU´RE AS STUBBORN
AS A TRUCK-STOP FAUCET,

05:01.301 --> 05:02.573
AND SO AM I!

05:02.573 --> 05:05.576
I´M GONNA WIN YOU BACK,
BENITA LOPEZ.

05:05.576 --> 05:08.739
UH, CALL YOU!
LOVE YOU!

05:13.384 --> 05:16.016
MEL, DO YOU
KNOW ABOUT YOUR SON?

05:16.016 --> 05:18.419
IF YOU WERE A VIETNAMESE
COCKTAIL WAITRESS

05:18.419 --> 05:19.620
WITH A DNA SAMPLE,

05:19.620 --> 05:23.824
THIS WOULD BE ONE HECK
OF A DEJA VU.

05:23.824 --> 05:25.325
YOUR SON, ZACK,

05:25.325 --> 05:27.628
HAS BEEN SNEAKING AROUND
BEHIND MY BACK

05:27.628 --> 05:28.929
AND SEEING CARMEN.

05:28.929 --> 05:31.331
WOW. MAN, THAT KID
GETS MORE...

05:32.563 --> 05:36.437
...SMART, CLASSY GIRLS
THAN HE DESERVES.

05:37.608 --> 05:38.969
LOOK, MEL,

05:38.969 --> 05:41.341
I DON´T WANT THIS TO AFFECT
OUR RELATIONSHIP,

05:41.341 --> 05:42.943
BUT ZACK GOT KICKED OUT
OF SCHOOL,

05:42.943 --> 05:44.545
AND HE GOT
A GIRL PREGNANT,

05:44.545 --> 05:46.777
AND I KIND OF DON´T
WANT HIM TO SEE MY DAUGHTER.

05:46.777 --> 05:48.078
OH, COME ON, GEORGE.

05:48.078 --> 05:50.080
YOU´RE BLOWING THIS
OUT OF PROPORTION.

05:50.080 --> 05:51.652
THEY´RE JUST A COUPLE
OF TEENAGE KIDS.

05:51.652 --> 05:53.424
IT WON´T LAST MORE THAN
A COUPLE OF WEEKS.

05:53.424 --> 05:55.586
A LOT CAN HAPPEN
IN A COUPLE OF WEEKS.

05:55.586 --> 05:58.659
SHE´S A 15-YEAR-OLD GIRL
WITH LOW SELF-ESTEEM.

05:58.659 --> 06:03.063
WELL, WHO DROPPED THE BALL
THERE, HUH, DADDY?

06:04.465 --> 06:06.637
MEL, TELL YOUR SON
TO STAY AWAY FROM MY DAUGHTER.

06:06.637 --> 06:09.369
GEORGE, THAT BOY DOESN´T LISTEN
TO A WORD I SAY.

06:09.369 --> 06:10.671
SO YOU´RE GONNA
LET HIM DO WHATEVER HE WANTS

06:10.671 --> 06:12.473
BECAUSE YOU´RE TOO AFRAID
TO BE A FATHER?

06:12.473 --> 06:15.406
WATCH IT, GEORGE.
I´M NOT AFRAID TO BE YOUR BOSS.

06:15.406 --> 06:16.947
REMEMBER WHO
YOU´RE TALKING TO.

06:16.947 --> 06:19.450
OKAY, LOOK, MEL,

06:19.450 --> 06:21.812
DON´T MAKE ME CHOOSE
BETWEEN MY JOB AND MY DAUGHTER,

06:21.812 --> 06:23.984
BECAUSE I´M IRRATIONAL
RIGHT NOW --

06:23.984 --> 06:25.886
TAMBIéN,
I´M LIGHTHEADED --

06:25.886 --> 06:27.858
AND I JUST MIGHT
PICK THE GIRL.

06:34.865 --> 06:37.428
IS CARMEN IN BACK?
I NEED TO TALK TO HER.

06:37.428 --> 06:40.501
NO, MISS CARMEN.
SHE NO HERE!

06:40.501 --> 06:43.133
BUT SHE JUST TEXT´D ME
TO MEET HER HERE.

06:43.133 --> 06:44.905
NO, SHE DON´T!

06:44.905 --> 06:47.077
THAT´S RIGHT,
IT´S ME, ERNIE.

06:58.088 --> 06:59.520
SIT DOWN.

07:03.924 --> 07:05.055
WHAT´S GOING ON?

07:05.055 --> 07:06.697
THE OWNER´S MY FRIEND.

07:06.697 --> 07:09.530
HE´S LETTING ME USE HIS PLACE
TO DEAL WITH A PROBLEM.

07:09.530 --> 07:11.101
MY DAD KNOWS I´M HERE.

07:11.101 --> 07:13.133
I DON´T CARE.

07:13.133 --> 07:14.905
YEAH, YOU KNOW WHAT?
ME EITHER.

07:14.905 --> 07:19.540
I GOT $15,000 IN THE BANK.
I´LL LIVE OFF THE INTEREST.

07:20.541 --> 07:23.974
ERNIE, THAT´S $300 A YEAR.

07:23.974 --> 07:26.016
SHE´S YOUR DAUGHTER,
YOU KNOW.

07:26.016 --> 07:27.548
I SHOULDN´T TALK SO BIG.

07:28.849 --> 07:30.180
LISTEN, MAN,

07:30.180 --> 07:32.222
I WARNED YOU
TO STAY AWAY FROM MY DAUGHTER,

07:32.222 --> 07:34.084
AND YOU DIDN´T,
SO I´M NOT WARNING ANYMORE.

07:34.084 --> 07:36.727
I WANT TO HEAR RIGHT NOW
THAT YOU´RE DONE WITH CARMEN.

07:38.088 --> 07:40.160
OKAY, MR. LOPEZ,

07:40.160 --> 07:42.993
BECAUSE YOU ASKED ME
SO NICELY...

07:42.993 --> 07:45.896
YOU HAVE MY WORD
THAT I WON´T SEE HER AGAIN.

07:45.896 --> 07:47.998
HEY, THIS IS WORKING.

07:47.998 --> 07:49.540
LISTEN TO ME, PUNK,

07:49.540 --> 07:51.241
´CAUSE I´M NOT
GONNA SAY IT AGAIN, OKAY?

07:51.241 --> 07:53.043
YOU´RE DONE SEEING MY DAUGHTER.
IT´S OVER.

07:53.043 --> 07:55.776
I THINK IT´LL BE OVER...

07:55.776 --> 07:58.478
WHEN CARMEN GETS OUT OF BED
TO MAKE ME A SANDWICH.

07:58.478 --> 07:59.780
NO, GEORGE!
GEORGE, NO!

07:59.780 --> 08:02.482
GEORGE, GEORGE,
IT´S NOT WORTH IT!

08:02.482 --> 08:04.585
NEXT TIME,
ERNIE´S NOT GONNA BE HERE!

08:12.563 --> 08:14.725
MAN.

08:14.725 --> 08:17.628
I REMEMBER WHEN THE NURSE
PUT CARMEN IN YOUR ARMS,

08:17.628 --> 08:20.671
AND YOU SAID, "OH, MY GOD,
SHE´S SO BEAUTIFUL.

08:20.671 --> 08:24.234
WHEN SHE STARTS DATING,
I´M NOT GONNA KNOW WHAT TO DO."

08:24.234 --> 08:27.978
AND I SAID,
"GEORGE, DON´T WORRY, MAN.

08:27.978 --> 08:30.240
WHEN THAT TIME COMES,
YOU´LL KNOW."

08:30.240 --> 08:32.212
WHAT´S YOUR POINT?

08:32.212 --> 08:34.184
WELL, I WANT TO APOLOGIZE.
YOU´RE RIGHT.

08:34.184 --> 08:41.191
YOU GOT NO IDEA
WHAT YOU´RE DOING.

08:51.201 --> 08:52.703
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

08:52.703 --> 08:54.134
I SAW CARMEN
WALKING UP THE DRIVEWAY.

08:54.134 --> 08:56.136
I WANTED TO CATCH
THE FIREWORKS.

08:57.938 --> 09:00.070
SO, HOW DOES IT FEEL?

09:00.070 --> 09:04.214
15 YEARS OF BAD PARENTING
ABOUT TO PAY OFF.

09:05.946 --> 09:09.950
15 YEARS
OF HOLLOW THREATS,

09:09.950 --> 09:13.553
SERIOUS,
DISAPPROVING LOOKS...

09:13.553 --> 09:16.286
THERE´S THE LOOK!

09:16.286 --> 09:18.058
MOM, GET OUT, OR ELSE.

09:18.058 --> 09:19.930
THERE´S THE HOLLOW THREAT!

09:21.792 --> 09:23.333
I DON´T BELIEVE YOU.

09:23.333 --> 09:24.995
SHOW TIME, MONKEYS!

09:24.995 --> 09:26.667
YOU CAN´T
THREATEN MY BOYFRIEND.

09:26.667 --> 09:28.999
THE FAKE, GAY, COVER BOYFRIEND
OR THE BOYFRIEND

09:28.999 --> 09:31.271
YOU´VE BEEN SEEING BEHIND
OUR BACKS FOR A MONTH?

09:31.271 --> 09:33.003
YOU READ MY DIARY?
I HATE YOU!

09:33.003 --> 09:34.274
I KNOW.

09:34.274 --> 09:36.346
IT´S WRITTEN
ON EVERY PAGE IN HERE.

09:36.346 --> 09:38.609
"I HATE DAD."
"GOD, I HATE DAD."

09:38.609 --> 09:41.181
"HEY, OLD LADY,
HANG UP THE MINISKIRT,

09:41.181 --> 09:42.753
YOU´RE NOT 15 ANYMORE."

09:42.753 --> 09:44.184
OH, THAT ONE´S ABOUT YOU.

09:46.116 --> 09:47.758
YOU HAD NO RIGHT
TO READ THIS.

09:47.758 --> 09:50.060
YOU LOST ALL YOUR RIGHTS
BY LYING TO US,

09:50.060 --> 09:52.062
AND IF WE HAVE TO LOOK
IN YOUR DIARY

09:52.062 --> 09:53.824
TO FIND THE TRUTH
ABOUT ZACK,

09:53.824 --> 09:55.125
WE´LL DO IT.

09:55.125 --> 09:57.297
OH, YOU WANT TO KNOW
THE TRUTH?

09:57.297 --> 09:59.329
I´M DATING ZACK BECAUSE I
LOVE HIM AND HE LOVES ME.

09:59.329 --> 10:00.671
CARMEN,
HE DOESN´T LOVE YOU.

10:00.671 --> 10:01.972
HE´S JUST USING YOU.

10:03.373 --> 10:06.036
HE TOLD ME HE WAS GONNA DUMP YOU
AS SOON AS HE GETS YOU IN BED!

10:06.036 --> 10:07.808
YOU´RE LYING.

10:07.808 --> 10:10.641
YOU HATE HIM SO MUCH, YOU´D SAY
ANYTHING TO KEEP US APART.

10:10.641 --> 10:12.643
DID I MAKE UP THAT HE
VANDALIZED THE FACTORY?

10:12.643 --> 10:14.645
THAT HE GOT A GIRL
PREGNANT?

10:14.645 --> 10:17.187
HE DIDN´T EVEN RESPECT THE GIRL
ENOUGH TO BE SAFE.

10:17.187 --> 10:18.849
NO, YOU GUYS
DON´T UNDERSTAND ZACK.

10:18.849 --> 10:20.320
HIS DAD WAS NEVER
THERE FOR HIM,

10:20.320 --> 10:22.052
AND HIS MOM´S
A BITTER, OLD DRUNK.

10:22.052 --> 10:23.754
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT THAT´S LIKE.

10:36.206 --> 10:39.009
YOU WANT TO
FIELD THAT ONE?

10:39.009 --> 10:42.342
OKAY, YOU KNOW WHAT?
END OF DISCUSSION, OKAY?

10:42.342 --> 10:44.344
WE DIDN´T
RAISE YOU THIS FAR

10:44.344 --> 10:46.376
SO YOU COULD SCREW UP YOUR LIFE
WITH ZACK.

10:46.376 --> 10:49.279
THERE IS NO WAY IN HELL YOU
ARE EVER GONNA SEE HIM AGAIN.

10:49.279 --> 10:51.321
YOU CAN´T STOP ME,
BECAUSE I´M ALMOST 16.

10:51.321 --> 10:53.353
I´M ALMOST A WOMAN.
I COULD DO WHATEVER I WANT.

10:53.353 --> 10:56.256
NOT AS LONG AS YOU LIVE
IN THIS HOUSE.

10:56.256 --> 10:58.658
IF YOU DON´T LIKE IT HERE,
GO LIVE SOMEWHERE ELSE.

10:58.658 --> 10:59.830
GEORGE, CALM DOWN.

10:59.830 --> 11:02.162
I´M TIRED
OF HER DISRESPECTING US.

11:02.162 --> 11:04.094
GO SEE WHAT IT´S LIKE
OUT THERE.

11:04.094 --> 11:05.736
SEND US A POSTCARD.

11:05.736 --> 11:06.997
GEORGE!

11:06.997 --> 11:09.039
AND DON´T EXPECT ME
TO COME LOOKING FOR YOU.

11:09.039 --> 11:10.801
I WISH YOU WEREN´T MY DAD.

11:13.744 --> 11:16.306
I´M GRADUATING!

11:16.306 --> 11:19.810
I PASSED
THE FIFTH GRADE!

11:19.810 --> 11:21.882
HONEY, THAT´S GREAT!

11:21.882 --> 11:24.254
WE´RE SO PROUD OF YOU.

11:24.254 --> 11:26.757
HEY, GRANDMA,
YOU MIGHT WANT TO STAND UP NOW,

11:26.757 --> 11:28.058
BECAUSE THOSE PIGS

11:28.058 --> 11:30.190
ARE GONNA BE FLYING
OUT OF YOUR BUTT.

11:38.398 --> 11:40.400
CARMEN IS LOCKED
IN HER ROOM.

11:40.400 --> 11:42.372
SHE STILL
WON´T TALK TO ME.

11:42.372 --> 11:44.334
YOU WENT TOO FAR
LAST NIGHT.

11:44.334 --> 11:46.136
LOOK, ANGIE,
SOMETIMES YOU HAVE TO

11:46.136 --> 11:49.139
GIVE KIDS AN ULTIMATUM
TO SCARE SOME SENSE INTO THEM.

11:49.139 --> 11:51.411
AND THAT WORKED
WHEN YOUR MOM DID IT TO YOU?

11:51.411 --> 11:52.783
YEAH.

11:52.783 --> 11:54.144
ONE TIME I REMEMBER
MY MOM SAYING,

11:54.144 --> 11:55.445
"HEY, IF YOU
DON´T LIKE IT HERE,

11:55.445 --> 11:57.087
I DON´T LIKE YOU HERE.
GET OUT."

11:57.087 --> 11:58.488
WHAT´D YOU DO?

11:58.488 --> 12:02.222
I STOPPED THROWING MY PEAS
OFF THE HIGH CHAIR.

12:02.222 --> 12:06.026
HONEY, DO YOU
WANT SOMETHING TO EAT?

12:06.026 --> 12:07.898
NAH, I´M JUST GOING
TO SCHOOL.

12:13.864 --> 12:15.165
WHAT´S THAT FOR?

12:15.165 --> 12:18.268
I´M SORRY, DADDY.

12:18.268 --> 12:21.171
I´M SORRY I LIED.

12:21.171 --> 12:23.313
I´LL STOP SEEING ZACK.

12:23.313 --> 12:26.176
OKAY, WELL, I´M SORRY
I HAD TO BE SO TOUGH ON YOU,

12:26.176 --> 12:28.478
BUT I ONLY DID IT
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU, OKAY?

12:28.478 --> 12:30.250
I KNOW.

12:32.452 --> 12:35.886
OKAY, WELL, I STILL
THINK YOU´RE WRONG ABOUT ZACK,

12:35.886 --> 12:38.829
BUT I GUESS UNTIL I´M 18,
I DON´T REALLY HAVE A CHOICE.

12:40.961 --> 12:43.133
HONEY...

12:43.133 --> 12:45.796
I KNOW YOU HAVE
A BROKEN HEART RIGHT NOW,

12:45.796 --> 12:48.899
BUT I PROMISE
YOU WILL GET THROUGH THIS, HUH?

12:50.801 --> 12:52.072
YEAH.

12:52.072 --> 12:55.275
I´LL SEE YOU
AT MAX´S GRADUATION.

13:00.280 --> 13:02.953
HUH?
HOW ABOUT THAT?

13:04.384 --> 13:06.216
NATURAL PARENT...

13:06.216 --> 13:08.218
[ WHISTLES ]

13:08.218 --> 13:10.320
BOOK PARENT.

13:11.922 --> 13:13.223
INSTINCTS...

13:16.997 --> 13:18.298
OPPOSITE OF INSTINCTS.

13:25.335 --> 13:27.237
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

13:27.237 --> 13:29.539
BENNY, DON´T SAY NOTHIN´.
JUST LISTEN.

13:32.242 --> 13:34.214
WHO ARE YOU CALLING?
THE POLICE.

13:34.214 --> 13:36.046
I´M GONNA REPORT
A JUSTIFIED HOMICIDE.

13:36.046 --> 13:38.448
HAND ME THOSE SCISSORS
OVER THERE, WOULD YOU?

13:40.220 --> 13:42.822
NOW, YOU LISTEN TO ME,
WOMAN!

13:44.895 --> 13:47.858
WHY SHOULD I EVER LISTEN TO YOU,
EVER, EVER AGAIN?

13:47.858 --> 13:50.430
YOU PRACTICALLY
WALKED OUT ON ME AT THE ALTAR

13:50.430 --> 13:52.202
FOR YOUR OLD GIRLFRIEND.

13:52.202 --> 13:54.264
I TOLD YOU,
I NEEDED TIME TO THINK.

13:54.264 --> 13:56.606
BUT NOW I KNOW.
I DON´T CARE ABOUT AMY.

13:56.606 --> 13:59.139
I DON´T CARE
ABOUT HAVING KIDS.

13:59.139 --> 14:00.340
ALL I CARE ABOUT

14:00.340 --> 14:03.443
IS SPENDING THE REST
OF MY LIFE WITH YOU.

14:08.148 --> 14:10.881
SO THAT´S IT, HUH?

14:10.881 --> 14:13.083
YOU EXPECT ME
TO JUST TAKE YOU BACK

14:13.083 --> 14:17.057
BECAUSE YOU HAVE DECIDED
THAT YOU ARE READY, HUH?!

14:17.057 --> 14:18.929
OKAY...

14:18.929 --> 14:23.563
WELL, I KNEW THIS WASN´T
GOING TO BE EASY,

14:23.563 --> 14:28.198
